Buffalo 68 cloudy; Charleston, S.C. 77 fair; Chattanooga 70 foggy;
Cincinnati 69 foggy; Cleveland 69 partly cloudy; Detroit 73 cloudy;
Hatteras 80 hazy; Jacksonville 71 foggy; Key West 83 partly cloudy;
